    "Similar to the enormous Chinese growth rates in numbers of papers and researchers, the number of HCRs has also increased: from seven in 2001 to 160 in 2014 (with a primary affiliation located in mainland China).",
    "On the institutional level, Li (2018) not only counted the institutional number of HCRs in China, but also the number of HCRs per 1000 academic faculty staff.",
    "This ratio reveals, e.g., a relative high value for the Tsinghua University in 2016, although the Chinese Academy of Science employs significantly more HCRs.",
